author: The Current
description:
Watch Samia and her band perform "Bovine Excision" in studio
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

Singer-songwriter Samia releases her second full-length album, 'Bloodless,' on April 25, 2025. Just a few weeks before the release, Samia visited The Current studio with some of her musical collaborators to perform four songs off the new album. Watch and listen to a performance of "Bovine Excision" above.

Musicians
Samia Finnerty – vocals
Sam Rosenstone – keyboards, vocals
Jake Luppen – electric guitar, vocals
Nathan Stocker – six- and 12-string guitar, vocals

author: The Current
description:
Watch Soccer Mommy (Sophie Allison) play "Still Clean" at The Current
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

Sophie Allison, best known by the musical moniker Soccer Mommy, released her latest album, 'Evergreen,' in October 2024. While on tour in support of the album, Soccer Mommy visited The Current to play solo versions of a couple songs from the new record along with one from her 2018 debut album, 'Clean.'

Watch and listen a performance of "Still Clean" above.

Sophia Allison – guitar, vocals
